UxMzI2Nzkg14iqrQUwADjJAUAXcggzMjMzMzI3MngAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "24_1637640560.610425", "card_id": "Q_500464929", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 44}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "昆明某公园内商贩疑似把「狗粮」当「鸥粮」售卖，这会对海鸥造成伤害吗？文明观鸥应该注意什么？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "最近，有市民发现海埂公园内的部分鸥粮售卖点不但捆绑销售鸥粮，甚至价格还高于建议零售价。 相关记者在走访调查过程中还在海洪湿地公园内，发现有商家售卖「三无」鸥粮，且以高价售卖，味道疑似「狗粮」。 经过专业鸥粮生产商辨别，该「三无」鸥粮非正规鸥粮，其表面还有一层厚厚的油脂，落入水里可能还会对水质造成污染。 目前，公园管理处工作人员已联系市场监督管理局，将按照相关制度进行执法。 昆明进入观鸥季，私自投喂不符合规范的食物会对海鸥造成什么影响？我们应该如何文明观鸥？离谱！「狗粮」当鸥粮在公园售卖？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-57f370ca0590aa34faa499a520776497_720w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "82 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/500464929"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4I/dyG2/K9m45EEAMaCDczNDk1NzI4ILTm5owGMAY4SkAYcgk1MDA0NjQ5Mjl4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "25_1637640560.6109908", "card_id": "Q_497114666", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 63}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "暗恋一个人对方会知道吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-c652cf8b80939760399e055bf4a7936b_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "80 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/497114666"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4I/dyG2/K9m45EEAMaCDcyNzUxMTU0ILWImowGMAA4dEAZcgk0OTcxMTQ2NjZ4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "26_1637640560.6112814", "card_id": "Q_500684207", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 48}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何看待诺基亚老年机可以用支付宝主动扫码？会帮助诺基亚逆势营销吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-df1ebfc72a0474969ea384ee6a6fd24f_720w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "79 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "